info.author: David Cramer
info.description:
# freight-cli

This is a command line interface to [Freight](https://github.com/getsentry/freight).

```bash
$ freight deploy example
Created new Task with ID = 1

$ freight tail -f 1
(waiting for output..)
# ...
```
